description.value:
This value set includes (at the end) some clinical observations, which may be relevant in a lab report (body weight, temperature ….).

**Value Set Definition:**

LOINC {



  {



    COMPONENT not containing the word "panel"



    STATUS in {ACTIVE}



    CLASSTYPE in                     {1}



    ORDER_OBS in {Observation, Both}



    CLASS exclude {CHALSKIN, H&P.HX.LAB, H&P.HX, LABORDERS, NR STATS, PATH.PROTOCOLS.*}



  }



  UNION



  {



    COMPONENT not ( containing the word "panel" OR starting with "can pronounce" )



    STATUS in {ACTIVE}



    CLASSTYPE in                     {2}



    ORDER_OBS in {Observation, Both}



    SYSTEM = ^Patient



  }



}
